jobDescription: Hey There! Jack Doby, LI's new premium eyewear brand, is looking for models! If you have a great look, personality and comfortable in front of the camera, please submit three photos to jackdobysocial@gmail.com We are having photoshoot this weekend on Long Island (6/16), all are encouraged to apply! (Sorry kids, 18+ only) Check out our website: www.jackdoby.com and our social pages: @jackdobyhq Model compensation will be in the form of free eyewear and retouched photos for model’s portfolio.
